Package: luwitemplate
Title: Unified Brand Styling for Shiny and ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lukas", "Willocx", , "lukaswillocx@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a complete styling system driven by a single '_brand.yml' 
    file. Create consistent Bootstrap themes for Shiny applications, ggplot2 
    visualizations, and interactive plotly charts with unified colors, fonts, 
    and styling. All components automatically share your brand identity.
